title: FINAL_QUIZ
position: 1040,2700
actor: ADULT_F
type: quiz
group: finale
---
<<set $quiz_score = 0>>
Which colors are on the Polish flags?
-> White and red.
	<<set $quiz_score = $quiz_score + 1>>
	Correct.
-> Blue and red.
	Not really. The Polish flag is white and red.
-> Green and white.
	Not really. The Polish flag is white and red.
Who was Chopin?
-> A composer.
	<<set $quiz_score = $quiz_score + 1>>
	Correct.
-> A football player.
	Not really. Chopin was a composer.
-> A king.
	Not really. Chopin was a composer.
