-> A river.
	<<set $quiz_score = $quiz_score + 1>>
	Correct.
-> A palace.
	Not really. The Wisla is a river.
-> A stadium.
	Not really. The Wisla is a river.
<<if $quiz_score >= 2>>
	Well done. You know enough about Warsaw.
	<<jump quest_end>>
<<else>>
	Good try. You can explore the city again and learn more.
<<endif>>
===

